,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T02:37:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你班垃圾自己讀唔成書就唔好以為其他人都讀唔到書啦</blockquote><br />\n求學問 無分種族優劣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8080699ffb067bb08b3cbe6b6070f2b82d119548","tid":314124,"uid":60635,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T02:38:24.000Z","msg":"有得看BBC 仲想點，我老母煩撚到看BBC 既機會都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f67d55c856c8af628610fe00e2966ec3ecb2253","tid":314124,"uid":69855,"like":3,"dislike":22,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T02:38:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f21e2761705791b8920169ceee861565c46ebcf7","tid":314124,"uid":34785,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T02:39:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>讀書 唔等如 搵到錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n女人黎講<br />\n條路係窄D<br />\n男既去做責鐵都得<br />\n女人要生得靚先易搵錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n白痴，我識大把公屋仔新移民讀完書做醫生</blockquote><br />\n一年香港出幾多醫生 大把 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n醫生係其中一樣啫，根本正常讀書然後讀三大神科唔難，出到黎揾四五萬根本係好正常，係d loser先會賴三賴四"},{"pid":"ec18cac718af9944eb8f7eec3c6dfac5f7b0c485","tid":314124,"uid":19990,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T02:39:45.000Z","msg":"港大醫學院每年入學的學生中住公屋多定私樓多"},{"pid":"9bed3d7e4627ea5c31cfd7c7cdc6d24151df882e","tid":314124,"uid":125171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T02:39:51.000Z","msg":"係大陸買得起小區樓應該唔窮嫁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b070cf158c8c0bc7276aef6e589ca0db10ecebea","tid":314124,"uid":41638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T02:40:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係大陸買得起小區樓應該唔窮嫁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小區都有分等級架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif