n<br />\n不過見親都係係band3讀讀住蝗話個啲垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以前中學隔離間band3全部都係蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"471fe2fd0b40499e1eca9fc0dc4ee9a13d8f3c23","tid":314124,"uid":65017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T05:54:40.000Z","msg":"咁你地點睇大陸果班爭香港大學學位既蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5058dd4b1fe4fd1bbed517b63bfa74b3c45b10e6","tid":314124,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T05:58:42.000Z","msg":"香港已經回歸中國廿年<br />\n點解系看前宗主國既BBC苦練英語!?<br />\n而唔系看現宗主國既CCTV苦練愛國???"},{"pid":"4f0a949fe1c882ecf55154163cc4fe2532b0e2b4","tid":314124,"uid":49383,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T06:08:05.000Z","msg":"係連登勤力都有罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddc07bd41e70757f35e13c32fb9918944b2af1ee","tid":314124,"uid":78336,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T06:17:39.000Z","msg":"係咪得我在意個句睇餐牌學英文 <br />\n真係仆得街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 睇到人地咁努力向上 <br />\n對比返連登班廢青日日怨天尤人真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9e4f3d224e79a312671496cd9e1aac85a43391b","tid":314124,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T06:20:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪得我在意個句睇餐牌學英文 <br />\n真係仆得街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 睇到人地咁努力向上 <br />\n對比返連登班廢青日日怨天尤人真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真😂<br />\n勤力又笑人蝗<br />\n跟本人地條件差你咁多都入ku"},{"pid":"6bfe3d14943b9306374d08d008a24663a29605e9","tid":314124,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T06:32:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔講其他<br />\n<br />\n其實29分可以揀理大三寶, 一樣係醫療<br />\n點解要貧埋hku 個名去讀非醫療理學士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"