,{"pid":"151d523712510616be0965a4db1152c78278139b","tid":314124,"uid":41638,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T07:04:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪得我在意個句睇餐牌學英文 <br />\n真係仆得街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 睇到人地咁努力向上 <br />\n對比返連登班廢青日日怨天尤人真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n角色調轉，連登仔根本無個份為爭上遊既堅定意志，見到間房細就番番上大陸了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講港獨 淨識怨天怨地 罵人地種族太過主動上進爭取自己好處<br />\n連登仔有幾多個有真係為港獨出過力<br />\n屌完人當爭取左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d28a2953f7c1f75867d9b68006019920d083ca0","tid":314124,"uid":65275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T07:08:15.000Z","msg":"刻苦耐勞 唔似連登班高屋仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5532e02c12d9aacacff57ebaaba60a0f2ccacc6e","tid":314124,"uid":77092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T07:09:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b4a772f937c2a6da0dca262a5fd99045a15fa683","tid":314124,"uid":87339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T07:12:06.000Z","msg":"29分 重讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49d20173802f1e3a274f8664292d32dc1bdaefba","tid":314124,"uid":53853,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T07:13:50.000Z","msg":"如果睇得多 BBC就學到英文<br />\n陽痿睇得多 av咩都醫得好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ad2c44e781067333f08c41495e07b4ff8b6b149","tid":314124,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T07:14:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果睇得多 BBC就學到英文<br />\n陽痿睇得多 av咩都醫得好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"8160d3c9569e5b3610eecea5c24670f047145cfb","tid":314124,"uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim